  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To investigate the glycosylated hemoglobin (HbA1c) control of Glimepiride (AMARYL) as OAD
      initiation mono-therapy in type 2 diabetic patients in China.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
